Description: 深き所まで征けば、何か面白い物が見つかるだろう。@{M}Travel deep enough, and you'll find something interesting.
LevelDescriptionText: 0|貴方は沼から帰還した！@{M}0|You've returned from the swamps!
ChangeDescriptionText: 10|悲鳴と身震いが…~20|夜の帳に目が…~30|広がる波紋が…~40|ぶら下がる茸が盗まれ…~50|肥えた白い蚊が…~60|悲鳴を上げるボタンインコが…~70|撹拌される硫黄が…~80|降り注ぐ蒸し暑い雨が…~90|苔生す竜骨が…~1|黒く粘つく泥が…~100|柔らかい燐光が…@{M}10|Shrieks and chitters...~20|Eyes in the undernight...~30|Spreading ripples...~40|Swags of hanging fungus...~50|Fat white mosquitoes...~60|Shrieking cockatoos...~70|Sulphurous stirrings...~80|A dribble of sticky rain...~90|A moss-furred boat-skeleton...~1|Black and stinking mud...~100|A soft phosphorescence...
Name: 後日談: 沼地を征く@{M}Another Day: Navigating the Swamps
